  "richContent": "<p>发车记录</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>【150】红利目前持有：共15份 = 13份富国中证红利 + 2份红利低波100 </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>【S】未交易，同步更新下图表</p>\n<p></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p></p>\n<p>PS：昨天红利低波指数涨幅0.00%，150/S分在了两天买，但“累计收益率%”和“买入净值”正巧也是一样的</p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn-community.qieman.com/F34FDCFD-C6F3-4C04-8B97-66F7F9041A1A.png\" />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-community.qieman.com/1BEAF49E-669E-4F05-8B15-CE35066DBCD5.png\" />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-community.qieman.com/7BA0944F-A182-48B9-B73E-B8F33627180A.png\" />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-community.qieman.com/F23665F2-8487-4493-89C2-EF642300B9BB.png\" />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-community.qieman.com/0A5F3EC2-131B-4FE7-B393-7E0C3709D1E7.png\" />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-community.qieman.com/08003164-062D-4D81-BF47-B4F29AB885A7.png\" />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-community.qieman.com/0CCA361A-2C9A-45B1-9BA8-74CA4CAEF7BF.png\" />",
